{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":159,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":null,"text":"快退进去！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":291,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_you_ren","speaker_name":"有人","listener":null,"text":"入口在这里！他们连铁盖子也没时间阖上。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":291,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_wei_liao","speaker_name":"尉缭","listener":"char_ying_zheng","text":"大王明鉴，刚才微臣贴地听声，发觉叛贼尚未离开地道，所以只要我们灌入浓烟，包保可歼灭部分叛贼。然后微臣再遣人循最接近这冢墓的城墙方向搜过去，找到出口，应可把叛贼一网成擒。","tone":"认真","chapter":291,"line_start":64,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":"char_ying_zheng","text":"大王开恩！","tone":"恐惧","chapter":291,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_wei_liao","speaker_name":"尉缭","listener":"char_li_si","text":"廷尉大人？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":291,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_wei_liao","speaker_name":"尉缭","listener":"char_ying_zheng","text":"大王请立即颁令，否则时机一去不返。","tone":"焦急","chapter":291,"line_start":86,"line_end":86},{"speaker":"char_wei_liao","speaker_name":"尉缭","listener":"char_ying_zheng","text":"大王为何只看着这里供奉的灵牌？","tone":"疑问","chapter":291,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_ying_zheng","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_wei_liao","text":"尉卿和其他人全给寡人退出去，只李卿一人留下。","tone":"严肃","chapter":291,"line_start":96,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_wei_liao","speaker_name":"尉缭","listener":"char_ying_zheng","text":"大王……","tone":"惊讶","chapter":291,"line_start":100,"line_end":100},{"speaker":"char_ying_zheng","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_wei_liao","text":"退下！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":291,"line_start":102,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_ying_zheng","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_li_si","text":"如何可教天下人不谈论这件事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":291,"line_start":106,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":"char_ying_zheng","text":"只要大王征服六国，统一天下，那时大王之令遍行大地，严谕谁敢提到项少龙三个字，谁就杀头，必然人人噤口，此事自然不了了之。","tone":"认真","chapter":291,"line_start":108,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_ying_zheng","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_li_si","text":"若他们嘴巴不说，却写成史书，有何法应付？","tone":"疑问","chapter":291,"line_start":112,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":"char_ying_zheng","text":"那时大王就坑那些人，烧他们写的书。","tone":"陈述","chapter":291,"line_start":114,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_ying_zheng","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_li_si","text":"吕不韦为项少龙所杀之事该如何处理？","tone":"疑问","chapter":291,"line_start":118,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":"char_ying_zheng","text":"这个更容易，说他畏罪逃回食邑，最后饮毒酒自尽。","tone":"陈述","chapter":291,"line_start":120,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_ying_zheng","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"师父！愿你一路平安！","tone":"温柔","chapter":291,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_ying_zheng","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":null,"text":"立即撤军！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":291,"line_start":128,"line_end":128}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiang_shao_long","name":"项少龙","alias":[],"identity":"主角，穿越者","faction":"乌家","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"穿越到秦朝的现代人，项少龙","personality":{"traits":["机智","勇敢","重情重义","灵活应变","有领导力"],"speech_style":"直接果断","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_ying_zheng","type":"师徒","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"从保护到分离"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[291],"source_refs":[{"chapter":291,"line_start":1,"line_end":159,"text":"项少龙的人仍有一半人未能进入地道"}]},{"id":"char_ying_zheng","name":"嬴政","alias":["小盘"],"identity":"秦王","faction":"秦国","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"未来的秦始皇，项少龙的徒弟","personality":{"traits":["雄才大略","果断","多疑","有野心","念旧"],"speech_style":"威严","temperament":"深沉"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"师徒","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"从依赖到独立"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[291],"source_refs":[{"chapter":291,"line_start":96,"line_end":128,"text":"小盘熟悉的声音终于响起道